This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D object detection using point cloud data. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as object detection is an important task in robotics. Additionally, the use of attention mechanism and deep learning techniques suggest that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as it uses the term "attention mechanism" which is commonly used in NLP.
